### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَعَلَى ٱلَّذِينَ هَادُوا۟ حَرَّمْنَا مَا قَصَصْنَا عَلَيْكَ مِن قَبْلُ ۖ وَمَا ظَلَمْنَـٰهُمْ وَلَـٰكِن كَانُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَهُمْ يَظْلِمُونَ</span>

### English

To the Jews, We have forbidden what We related to you before. We did not wrong them, but it was they who wronged themselves.